Package net.dean.jraw.managers

Contains all classes that manage certain parts of the API

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractManager
    This class serves as the base class for all "manager" classes, which have control over a certain section of the API, such as multireddits, wikis, and messages
    AccountManager
    This class manages common user actions, such as voting, commenting, saving, etc.
    AccountManager.SubmissionBuilder
    This class provides a way to configure posting parameters of a new submission
    InboxManager
    This class is responsible for managing a user's inbox
    ModerationManager
    This class manages actions most commonly reserved for moderators (although some of them can be used on yourself without moderator powers).
    MultiRedditManager
    This class provides the ability to create, read, update, and delete multireddits.
    ThingCache
    Maintains a map of Thing names and Things inside of WeakReferences.
    WikiManager
    This class is responsible for managing a wiki
